  "howToDecideBackupTitle": "Kaise decide karein",
  "@howToDecideBackupTitle": {
    "description": "Title for how to decide backup method modal"
  },
  "howToDecideBackupText1": "Sabse aam wajah jisme log apna Bitcoin kho dete hain woh hai physical backup kho jaana. Jo bhi aapka physical backup dhundh le woh aapka saara Bitcoin le sakta hai. Agar aapko pura yakeen hai ki aap ise achhe se chhupa sakte ho aur kabhi nahi khooge, toh yeh ek achha tarika hai.",
  "@howToDecideBackupText1": {
    "description": "First paragraph explaining backup method decision"
  },
  "howToDecideBackupText2": "Encrypted vault aapko choroon se bachata hai jo backup churana chahte hain. Yeh aapko backup galti se kho jaane se bhi bachata hai kyunki yeh aapke cloud mein store hoga. Google ya Apple jaisi cloud storage companies aapke Bitcoin tak nahi pahunch sakti kyunki encryption password bahut mazboot hai. Ek chhoti si sambhaavna hai ki web server jo aapke backup ki encryption key store karta hai use hack kiya ja sakta hai. Agar aisa hua toh aapke cloud account mein backup suraksha khtre mein pad sakti hai.",
  "@howToDecideBackupText2": {
    "description": "Second paragraph explaining encrypted vault benefits and risks"
  },
  "physicalBackupRecommendation": "Physical backup: ",
  "@physicalBackupRecommendation": {
    "description": "Bold label for physical backup recommendation"
  },
  "physicalBackupRecommendationText": "Aapko apni khud ki operational security capabilities par pura yakeen hai ki aap Bitcoin seed words chhupa kar rakh sako.",
  "@physicalBackupRecommendationText": {
    "description": "Text explaining when to use physical backup"
  },
  "encryptedVaultRecommendation": "Encrypted vault: ",
  "@encryptedVaultRecommendation": {
    "description": "Bold label for encrypted vault recommendation"
  },
  "encryptedVaultRecommendationText": "Aap nishchit nahi ho aur backup security practices seekhne ke liye zyada waqt chahiye.",
  "@encryptedVaultRecommendationText": {
    "description": "Text explaining when to use encrypted vault"
  },
  "visitRecoverBullMessage": "Zyada jaankari ke liye recoverbull.com visit karo.",
  "@visitRecoverBullMessage": {
    "description": "Message with link to more information"
  },
  "howToDecideVaultLocationText1": "Google ya Apple jaisi cloud storage companies aapke Bitcoin tak nahi pahunch sakti kyunki encryption password bahut mazboot hai. Woh sirf tab aapke Bitcoin le sakti hain jab woh key server (online service jo encryption password store karta hai) ke saath mil jayein. Agar key server kabhi hack hua toh aapka Bitcoin Google ya Apple cloud ke saath khtre mein pad sakta hai.",
  "@howToDecideVaultLocationText1": {
    "description": "First paragraph explaining vault location decision"
  },
  "howToDecideVaultLocationText2": "Custom location bahut zyada surakshit ho sakti hai, yeh is baat par nirbhar karta hai ki aap kaunsi jagah chunte ho. Aapko backup file kho jaane se bhi bachna hoga aur device nahi kho sakte jisme backup file hai.",
